{"title_page": "Jerry van Ewijk", "text_new": "{{Infobox football biography\n| name          = Jerry van Wolfgang\n| image          = \n| birth_date    = {{birth date and age|1992|03|12|df=y}}\n| birth_place = [[Arnhem]], [[Netherlands]]\n| height         = {{height|m=1.75}}\n| position       = [[Winger (association football)|Winger]]\n| currentclub    = [[Cheonan City FC]]\n| clubnumber     = 7\n| youthyears1 = \n| youthclubs1 = Vitesse 1892\n| youthyears2 = 2001\u20132008\n| youthclubs2 = [[PSV Eindhoven|PSV]]\n| youthyears3 = 2008\u20132011\n| youthclubs3 = [[SBV Vitesse|Vitesse]]/[[AGOVV Apeldoorn|AGOVV]] \n| years1 = 2011\u20132012 \n| clubs1 = [[AGOVV Apeldoorn|AGOVV]] \n| caps1 = 20 \n| goals1 = 1\n| years2 = 2012\u20132015 \n| clubs2 = [[De Graafschap]] \n| caps2 = 72 \n| goals2 = 24\n| years3 = 2015\u20132016 \n| clubs3 = [[Go Ahead Eagles]] \n| caps3 = 26 \n| goals3 = 6\n| years4 = 2017    \n| clubs4 = [[Orange County SC]] \n| caps4 = 29\n| goals4 = 8\n| years5 = 2018 \n| clubs5 = [[Reno 1868]] \n| caps5 = 27\n| goals5 = 6\n| years6 = 2019 \n| clubs6 = [[Orange County SC]] \n| caps6 = 33\n| goals6 = 3\n| years7 = 2020\u2013 \n| clubs7 = [[Cheonan City FC]] \n| caps7 = 0\n| goals7 = 0\n| nationalyears1 = 2009\n| nationalteam1 = [[Netherlands national under-17 football team|Netherlands U-17]]\n| nationalcaps1 = 10\n| nationalgoals1 = 0\n| nationalyears2 = 2010\u20132011\n| nationalteam2 = [[Netherlands national under-19 football team|Netherlands U-19]]\n| nationalcaps2 = 3\n| nationalgoals2 = 0\n| pcupdate = 25 October 2019\n}}\n'''Jerry van Wolfgang''' (previously known as '''Jerry van Ewijk''')<ref>https://www.angelsonparade.com/2019/2/11/18220660/orange-county-sc-bring-back-jerry-van-wolfgang-ewijk-reno-1868</ref> (born 12 March 1992) is a [[Netherlands|Dutch]] footballer who plays as a [[Winger (association football)|winger]] for [[Cheonan City FC]].\n\n==Club career==\nHe made his professional debut for [[AGOVV Apeldoorn]] and joined [[De Graafschap]] on non-professional terms in 2012.<ref>[https://www.superboeren.nl/news/1063-jerry-van-ewijk-naar-de-graafschap Jerry van Ewijk naar De Graafschap] \u2013 Superboeren {{in lang|nl}}</ref> He scored 18 goals for the ''Superboeren'' in the 2014/15 season and moved to relegated [[Go Ahead Eagles]] at the end of that season.<ref>[http://www.omroepgelderland.nl/nieuws/2095055/Jerry-van-Ewijk-wil-topscorer-worden-van-Jupiler-League Jerry van Ewijk wil topscorer worden van Jupiler League] \u2013 Omroep Gelderland {{in lang|nl}}</ref> With both De Graafschap and Go Ahead he won promotion to the [[Eredivisie]].\n\nVan Ewijk moved abroad to play for [[United Soccer League]] side [[Orange County SC|Orange County]] in January 2017.<ref>[http://www.ga-eagles.nl/orange-county-nieuwe-club-jerry-ewijk/ Orange County nieuwe club Jerry van Ewijk] \u2013 GA Eagles {{in lang|nl}}</ref>\n\nAfter playing the 2018 season with [[Reno 1868 FC]], van Ewijk rejoined Orange County on 11 February 2019.<ref>{{cite web |title=ORANGE COUNTY SC SIGNS WINGER JERRY VAN WOLFGANG |url=https://www.orangecountysoccer.com/news_article/show/994004 |website=OrangeCountySoccer.com |accessdate=11 February 2019}}</ref>\n\n==International career==\nVan Ewijk played 10 matches for the [[Netherlands national under-17 football team|Netherlands U-17 team]] including 3 at the [[2009 UEFA European Under-17 Championship]].<ref>[http://www.onsoranje.nl/teams/184965/speler/5986/loopbaan KNVB U17 profile] \u2013 Ons Oranje</ref>\nHe also played 3 games for the [[Netherlands national under-19 football team|Netherlands U-19s]].<ref>[http://www.onsoranje.nl/toernooien/966/selectie/185189/speler/5986/loopbaan KNVB U19 profile] \u2013 Ons Oranje</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* [http://www.vi.nl/spelers/carriere/jerry-van-ewijk.htm Voetbal International profile] {{in lang|nl}}\n*{{Soccerway|jerry-van-ewijk/199301}}\n\n\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Ewijk, Jerry}}\n[[Category:1992 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Sportspeople from Arnhem]]\n[[Category:Association football wingers]]\n[[Category:Dutch footballers]]\n[[Category:AGOVV Apeldoorn players]]\n[[Category:De Graafschap players]]\n[[Category:Go Ahead Eagles players]]\n[[Category:Orange County SC players]]\n[[Category:Reno 1868 FC players]]\n[[Category:Eerste Divisie players]]\n[[Category:USL Championship players]]\n[[Category:Dutch expatriate footballers]]\n[[Category:Expatriate soccer players in the United States]]\n[[Category:Dutch expatriate sportspeople in the United States]]\n\n\n{{Netherlands-footy-forward-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox football biography\n| name          = Jerry van Wolfgang\n| image          = \n| birth_date    = {{birth date and age|1992|03|12|df=y}}\n| birth_place = [[Arnhem]], [[Netherlands]]\n| height         = {{height|m=1.75}}\n| position       = [[Winger (association football)|Winger]]\n| currentclub    = [[Cheonan City FC]]\n| clubnumber     = 7\n| youthyears1 = \n| youthclubs1 = Vitesse 1892\n| youthyears2 = 2001\u20132008\n| youthclubs2 = [[PSV Eindhoven|PSV]]\n| youthyears3 = 2008\u20132011\n| youthclubs3 = [[SBV Vitesse|Vitesse]]/[[AGOVV Apeldoorn|AGOVV]] \n| years1 = 2011\u20132012 \n| clubs1 = [[AGOVV Apeldoorn|AGOVV]] \n| caps1 = 20 \n| goals1 = 1\n| years2 = 2012\u20132015 \n| clubs2 = [[De Graafschap]] \n| caps2 = 72 \n| goals2 = 24\n| years3 = 2015\u20132016 \n| clubs3 = [[Go Ahead Eagles]] \n| caps3 = 26 \n| goals3 = 6\n| years4 = 2017    \n| clubs4 = [[Orange County SC]] \n| caps4 = 29\n| goals4 = 8\n| years5 = 2018 \n| clubs5 = [[Reno 1868]] \n| caps5 = 27\n| goals5 = 6\n| years6 = 2019 \n| clubs6 = [[Orange County SC]] \n| caps6 = 33\n| goals6 = 3\n| years7 = 2020- \n| clubs7 = [[Cheonan City FC]] \n| caps7 = 0\n| goals7 = 0\n| nationalyears1 = 2009\n| nationalteam1 = [[Netherlands national under-17 football team|Netherlands U-17]]\n| nationalcaps1 = 10\n| nationalgoals1 = 0\n| nationalyears2 = 2010\u20132011\n| nationalteam2 = [[Netherlands national under-19 football team|Netherlands U-19]]\n| nationalcaps2 = 3\n| nationalgoals2 = 0\n| pcupdate = 25 October 2019\n}}\n'''Jerry van Wolfgang''' (previously known as '''Jerry van Ewijk''')<ref>https://www.angelsonparade.com/2019/2/11/18220660/orange-county-sc-bring-back-jerry-van-wolfgang-ewijk-reno-1868</ref> (born 12 March 1992) is a [[Netherlands|Dutch]] footballer who plays as a [[Winger (association football)|winger]] for [[Orange County SC]] in the [[USL Championship]].\n\n==Club career==\nHe made his professional debut for [[AGOVV Apeldoorn]] and joined [[De Graafschap]] on non-professional terms in 2012.<ref>[https://www.superboeren.nl/news/1063-jerry-van-ewijk-naar-de-graafschap Jerry van Ewijk naar De Graafschap] - Superboeren {{in lang|nl}}</ref> He scored 18 goals for the ''Superboeren'' in the 2014/15 season and moved to relegated [[Go Ahead Eagles]] at the end of that season.<ref>[http://www.omroepgelderland.nl/nieuws/2095055/Jerry-van-Ewijk-wil-topscorer-worden-van-Jupiler-League Jerry van Ewijk wil topscorer worden van Jupiler League] - Omroep Gelderland {{in lang|nl}}</ref> With both De Graafschap and Go Ahead he won promotion to the [[Eredivisie]].\n\nVan Ewijk moved abroad to play for [[United Soccer League]] side [[Orange County SC|Orange County]] in January 2017.<ref>[http://www.ga-eagles.nl/orange-county-nieuwe-club-jerry-ewijk/ Orange County nieuwe club Jerry van Ewijk] - GA Eagles {{in lang|nl}}</ref>\n\nAfter playing the 2018 season with [[Reno 1868 FC]], van Ewijk rejoined Orange County on 11 February 2019.<ref>{{cite web |title=ORANGE COUNTY SC SIGNS WINGER JERRY VAN WOLFGANG |url=https://www.orangecountysoccer.com/news_article/show/994004 |website=OrangeCountySoccer.com |accessdate=11 February 2019}}</ref>\n\n==International career==\nVan Ewijk played 10 matches for the [[Netherlands national under-17 football team|Netherlands U-17 team]] including 3 at the [[2009 UEFA European Under-17 Championship]].<ref>[http://www.onsoranje.nl/teams/184965/speler/5986/loopbaan KNVB U17 profile] - Ons Oranje</ref>\nHe also played 3 games for the [[Netherlands national under-19 football team|Netherlands U-19s]].<ref>[http://www.onsoranje.nl/toernooien/966/selectie/185189/speler/5986/loopbaan KNVB U19 profile] - Ons Oranje</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* [http://www.vi.nl/spelers/carriere/jerry-van-ewijk.htm Voetbal International profile] {{in lang|nl}}\n*{{Soccerway|jerry--van-ewijk/199301}}\n\n\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Ewijk, Jerry}}\n[[Category:1992 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Sportspeople from Arnhem]]\n[[Category:Association football wingers]]\n[[Category:Dutch footballers]]\n[[Category:AGOVV Apeldoorn players]]\n[[Category:De Graafschap players]]\n[[Category:Go Ahead Eagles players]]\n[[Category:Orange County SC players]]\n[[Category:Reno 1868 FC players]]\n[[Category:Eerste Divisie players]]\n[[Category:USL Championship players]]\n[[Category:Dutch expatriate footballers]]\n[[Category:Expatriate soccer players in the United States]]\n[[Category:Dutch expatriate sportspeople in the United States]]\n\n\n{{Netherlands-footy-forward-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Milkloverfan", "label": "safe", "comment": "fixeddashesusing ascript", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jerry_van_Ewijk"}
